### Describe the bug

When using observeQuery, it appears on local element update, only partial fields from the model are being returned, and the remaining fields are just not propagated through the snapshot callback.

### Expected behavior

I'd expect the full model to be returned, since we return all matching elements from the query as part of the response. I have confirmed that in IndexedDB the full model is updated and appears to be complete.

